Usage: setExportMode [-help] [-reset] [-fullPinout {true|false}]
                     [-implicitPortMapping {true|false}]

-help                                 # Prints out the command usage
-reset                                # Resets all or specified options to default value
-fullPinout {true|false}              # Output all pins. (bool, default=false)
-implicitPortMapping {true|false}     # Do implicit port mapping.
                                      # (bool, default=false)